{"id":"810717281101496320","type":"text","timestamp":1773160248,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/810717281101496320","is_reblog":true,"added_content":true,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://jewishbarbies.tumblr.com/post/797787957578842112/ive-been-laughing-at-fuck-this-lemon-you-take\">jewishbarbies</a>:</p><blockquote><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"217\" data-orig-width=\"516\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d369e9bf515471c405343462015eb71c/f64e1b2f2b6ba0b7-cb/s640x960/2f0b5a59815565267673904d54479816928788f9.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"217\" data-orig-width=\"516\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d369e9bf515471c405343462015eb71c/f64e1b2f2b6ba0b7-cb/s75x75_c1/af389623a09aa0289ced5bfbd20a1000a0a49a31.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d369e9bf515471c405343462015eb71c/f64e1b2f2b6ba0b7-cb/s100x200/674d97325d04b8ea64a53f8517206797ade73a83.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d369e9bf515471c405343462015eb71c/f64e1b2f2b6ba0b7-cb/s250x400/5560a2fbaf519569bfb179fc99dda56f6a85cf3c.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d369e9bf515471c405343462015eb71c/f64e1b2f2b6ba0b7-cb/s400x600/b92132f734131ccc46195958f1d394625993ae30.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d369e9bf515471c405343462015eb71c/f64e1b2f2b6ba0b7-cb/s500x750/c264a7b9c908bf1ff156d118865bae715ca5f584.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/d369e9bf515471c405343462015eb71c/f64e1b2f2b6ba0b7-cb/s540x810/aa03a4e652b6b3c7589decf72d9f2952ff7775d8.jpg 516w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 516px) 100vw, 516px\"/></figure></div><p>I’ve been laughing at “fuck this lemon you take it” for several minutes</p></blockquote>\n<p>They are just following instructions from the late great Cave Johnson:</p><p class=\"npf_quote\">“When life gives you lemons, don’t make lemonade. Make life take the lemons back! Get mad! I don’t want your damn lemons, what the hell am I supposed to do with these? Demand to see life’s manager! Make